            "chapterTitle": "The Excellence of As-Salat (The Prayer)",
            "urn": 1620860,
            "body": "<p>Jabiru (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"The similitude of the five (obligatory) Salat is like a river running at the door of one of you in which he takes a bath five times a day.\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.</p>",
            "grades": []
